description: Bea's Soda Bar is bringing you the best of your favorite bubbly beverage! A soda fountain out of yesteryear, with modern mobile style, Bea's has handcrafted soda creations like nobody else. Along with their gourmet shaved ice, waffles, and a rotating menu of culinary treats, Bea's Soda Bar offers a great, friendly atmosphere and some local charm. Stop by and experience your new favorite mobile eatery today!
name: Bea's Soda Bar
